BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 464 Tm (This project is a legal document summarization MVP for long court judgments and legal) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 450 Tm (opinions. It accepts TXT or PDF documents, preprocesses and segments them, predicts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 436 Tm (rhetorical roles, generates multiple abstractive summary candidates, reranks them with) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 422 Tm (argument-aware scoring, and returns the best summary with metrics and interpretable) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 408 Tm (reasoning.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 391 Tm (The project is inspired by the ACL 2023 paper on argument-aware abstractive summarization) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 377 Tm (with summary reranking, but it is implemented as a practical local-first engineering system) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 363 Tm (rather than a one-to-one reproduction of the paper's exact experimental setup.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 346 Tm (Core Problem Statement) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 322 Tm (Legal opinions are difficult to summarize because:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 305 Tm (- they are long and often exceed the context length of standard models) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 289 Tm (- key information is distributed across facts, issue, arguments, analysis, statutes, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 275 Tm (ruling) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 259 Tm (- legal usefulness depends not only on fluency but also on preserving the court's) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 245 Tm (reasoning path) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 229 Tm (- citations, section headers, numbers, and procedural history can matter a lot) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 213 Tm (A plain summarizer may produce readable text but still miss the most important legal) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 199 Tm (structure. This system tries to solve that by making summary selection aware of rhetorical) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 52 185 Tm (and argumentative content.) Tj ET
