BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 473 Tm (- multiple candidate summaries are better than blindly trusting a single decode) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 457 Tm (- reranking should use argument or rhetorical information) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 441 Tm (- long-document chunking is important) Tj ET
