BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 384 Tm (- hybrid role classification rather than an exact paper-specific supervised pipeline) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 368 Tm (- practical faithfulness proxies instead of a research-only scoring function) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 352 Tm (- local-first UI, API, exports, auth, scripts, tests, and Docker support) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.12 0.16 0.22 rg 1 0 0 1 60 336 Tm (- CPU-safe fallback behavior) Tj ET
